Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周终于到修学旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去京都 四日三夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必需品和注意事项大家自己看指南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都的女生 应该很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}听到了 别兴奋过头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你无缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计说了也没用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被其他学校的人搭讪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己学校的人都没戏 还想外校的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的修学旅行 我还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好玩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上还会轮流说自己心上人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心上人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心上人就是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可告人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可告人×N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田是不是第一次去京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古都啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店肯定也充满历史情调
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去开房吧 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有诅咒说修学旅行好上的 很快就散的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我跟小须田只需要打一炮就行了 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把铅笔跟吸管搞错了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动摇得很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00E1B80F&}万岁！修学旅行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没能单独在一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 修学旅行是咋样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是集体活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难跟小山田二人世界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然能理解你想跟她再亲一次的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 ~ 虽然想啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥知道我们亲过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没提起过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲第二次之前 还有更重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真向人家表白过没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你这样子 无论过多久 都只是暧昧关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人啊 个个都希望对方把心意说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来...对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没考虑过山田的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受了 亲嘴什么的想上就上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想上就上...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奸笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 这话题是纯还是不纯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾化妆水 刷牙套装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 有好好在准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 京都的导游手册？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}京都酒店导游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha ha ha这是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第14号线 7点40分发车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 好困
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田 你趁现在先好好讴歌一下纯洁的青春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为三天后 你的童子功就会被我废了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行晚上的咸湿话题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从听话人变成发言人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被人拿来当话题的 这都不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and Gentlemen we will soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 去京都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是在路上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉算点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 还有醋拌海带巧克力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 超难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要温热咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务员 我要啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有人想马上就退学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy过头最后倒大霉的家伙 还真有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小须田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田 我们也要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你邮箱地址 过后给我发哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 这不是数码相机啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田 我们也要 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田那家伙 别以为自己是负责拍照的就很受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是全都是京都名产啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田 帮我把行李放上架子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田 帮我揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是没误会 不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为啥感觉也很不爽...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人心真复杂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是电影村的小册子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去年我妈去过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 好不好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说玩得相当happy来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对话自然而然就多起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的台词也比平常多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过表白就难了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不能跟她单独在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田也帮我们拍一拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍得好看点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还没有表白的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田 来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老拍别人 也留几张自己的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我帮你跟山田拍一张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁 谁要跟那种爱误会的叛徒拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么所谓 大家都在拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...想拍 想跟山田一起拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 站起来排一块
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只此一张哦 我特别开恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是修学旅行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了哦 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅馆了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都齐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天是集体活动 没办法开溜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了好久 机会都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水寺也不是很高嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对古人来说可是划时代的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到京都观个毛光啊 都不想想我这边这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古都千年的历史都比不上打炮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待去泡温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道京都料理是怎样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 说到京都的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京怀石料理 家常菜 京都点心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都的食物太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田才不是那种被食物支配的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得自己像个傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才一直没察觉我的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫野你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下 你胸又大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 笨蛋 在摸哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生应该会干这些吧 小须田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小须田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大...你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来比鸟大赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生那边 应该会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想？ 刚才那些话全是你的妄想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关灯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好睡觉 备战明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等好久了 修学旅行夜晚 当然就是咸湿话题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 竹下 你的头炮是啥感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice 三乡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:09:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实她都没详细告诉过我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下 你跟现任男友很长久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被锁定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算防守森严的女人也会被气氛压倒 赤裸裸地激烈告白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是修学旅行的妙趣所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光说我一个 太狡猾了 三乡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还没试过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那就换片濑的来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得你头炮是在酒店打的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 你不是知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店？ 该不会穿着校服就进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说就是啦 不能被人随便捏造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三乡 山田 你们过后给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…最开始首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你们还不快点睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下她啊 为了纪念初中毕业到男朋友的房闻...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 片濑又咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想多了解山田一点...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如她喜欢什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然表白也很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样跟她一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起感受也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边是本殿 那边是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她喜欢寺庙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来的好后院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带小须田来这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么叫他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 用短信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦跟往常不一样 能坦白传达自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18}标题 建立肉体关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18}现在能不能单独见面？\N一起打炮吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信？ 谁发的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 短信求交配的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 赶紧回我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 估计一辈子都不会回你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家一起坐禅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱散烦恼 不被杂念困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心神涣散的人 就打一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打以后 要行礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨打了还要行礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽 女王大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼来得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没机会向山田表白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 只要能表白的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心 推倒我吧 小须田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有没烦恼啊 这个犹豫不决的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念没有一丝紊乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位少女 已经领会禅之道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 啊 ~ 哥哥 ~ 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让山田说不出话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 虽然内心的烦恼在涡旋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却毫不泄露出外头 恐怖的精神力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说 人的烦恼有108种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过抛除烦恼 就会看到自己真正追求的路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己真正追求的路...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 打炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 跟小须田 打炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害！没有丝毫迷惘 这一位已经悟道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家左边看到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼印观光 京都支社大厦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我听导游小姐解说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没能跟他独处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木筏观光以后 就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连有没有表白机会都不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来这三天 跟小须田一点进展都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 在船上诱惑他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回程电车上说不定...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 我已经把持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 得快点上船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H00E1B80F&}山田、我喜……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路吵架的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 两位客人把船包下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 就我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是诱惑小须田的绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傻嘛我 区区小须田 牵个手就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能跟她独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格来说不算是二人世界啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种景色优美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行这算是最后一站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错过这个机会 大概到毕业都表白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就擦肩而过 十年左右过后...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁 你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新来的 不准偷懒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 我不要那种未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 手 得牵手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就摸那里？！不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有回去（青蛙）了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}蛙岩(笑)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是冷笑话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样结束好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这么远的地方 两人独处却什么都没发生就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田就没所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的修学旅行 一生只有一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 我喜...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就对你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田这种笨蛋就给我掉下河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}电视机前的好孩子千万不要模仿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行就结束了啊 太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想跟女生搞好一点关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没戏没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来也没能跟其他学校的女生搭讪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无斩获
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}喂 山田...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 整个修学旅行跟小须田毫无进展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 听说你跟小须田两个木筏观光来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 我跟那种挫男会发生什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起 太好了 什么都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥要生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田 别这么郁闷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是能跟山田一起 已经很荣幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫身份不相配
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肉真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份不相配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以山田才会那么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人表白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定只会给她添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须由 没事吧 没食欲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉 我要了行么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在自己这边 友情也不咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到东京 要不要到我家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 可以啊 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵个毛 修学旅行的情侣马上就散的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不想服输也别那么大声啊 虽然是挺惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 看那样子是没发生好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还认识了其他学校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还买了礼物给哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 宫野 买了好多手信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 给家人的 香月姐的 给小须田的也买了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的要给他的话 就是怪人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 三乡有没碰到什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他学校的男生跟我搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是问 金阁寺是那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}东京 ~ 东京 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散 别到处乱跑直接回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 到家之前都还算修学旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹下 陪我去借可乐消愁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 过后我有约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人吗 是要会情郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是松尾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后 什么都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田不是喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得好愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是换个目标吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...小须田？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一班电车么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来换乘前就在追你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要救差点被人潮挤倒的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被人误会成痴汉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像小须田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田原来在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田原来在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管 对你又没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就对你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 对你 对你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜！喜一一！喜一一！欢...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 我成功了 终于成功表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然样子很逊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就清爽了 无论山田有什么回覆 都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能听清
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su su
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明内衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裸王？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 应该是“喜欢”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是特意追上我都要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死小须田 不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心死了 你这个摄影宅跑腿男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要遮羞也不用这么激动...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛 这已经跟能打炮无疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有那么点开心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 等等 说不定其实完全不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别素颜朝天了 皮肤都开裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话 死小须田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打完炮后给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之还是很想干一场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,su？ su呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是 “好色鬼”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者是“色狼”之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不喜欢上我的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要怎么回覆他？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？ 回覆？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都表白了 你也得给个答覆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如“我也喜欢你”之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 为啥我要说这话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这时候还嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者给他发张朋友卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮 炮友卡的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮友不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 要说讨厌他么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是逼太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 说讨厌他的话 不就打不成炮了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表白是表白了 不知道有没把心意传达给她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得认真问问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我怎么逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川流不息 然其水非原水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（*出自《方丈记》）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮沫漂于积水 此消彼起未可久存…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小须田 有些话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的话 午休在社团活动室等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是回覆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道是喜欢还是讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想打炮罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小须田这笨蛋！
